<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Celebrate" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Celebrate,</orth> to perform solemnly: <cit><quote>a contract of true love to c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 84</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 84</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.204" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 204</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 5.3.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 3, 80</bibl>. <cit><quote>more than my dancing soul doth c. this feast of battle,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.91" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 91</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.6.14" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 6, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 159</bibl>. <cit><quote>and c. our drink,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 7, 111</bibl></cit>.
